React ka useEffect hook side effects ko manage karne ke liye use hota hai. Yeh component ke render hone ke baad kisi bhi function ko call karne ki sahulat deta hai. Aap isko data fetch karne, subscriptions set karne ya manually DOM manipulate karne ke liye use kar sakte hain. Iski syntax kuch is tarah hai: 

```javascript
import React, { useEffect } from 'react';

function MyComponent() {
    useEffect(() => {
        // Ye code component ke render hone ke baad chalega
        console.log('Component mounted');
        return () => {
            // Ye code component ke unmount hone par chalega
            console.log('Component unmounted');
        };
    }, []); // Empty array matlab sirf mount aur unmount par chalega

