JavaScript mein async/await asynchronous programming ko asan banata hai. `async` function define karne se yeh function promise return karta hai. Aur `await` ka istemal kisi promise ka result lene ke liye hota hai jab tak wo complete na ho jaye. Iska istemal karne se code ka flow synchronous jaisa nazar aata hai. Yahan ek example hai: 

```javascript
