Queue ek linear data structure hai jo First In First Out (FIFO) principle par kaam karta hai. Matlab jo pehle aata hai, wo pehle nikalta hai. Queue ko implement karne ke liye hum array ya linked list ka istemal kar sakte hain. Yahan pe ek simple queue ka example diya gaya hai:

```python
class Queue:
    def __init__(self):
        self.items = []

    def is_empty(self):
        return len(self.items) == 0

    def enqueue(self, item):
        self.items.append(item)

    def dequeue(self):
        return self.items.pop(0) if not self.is_empty() else None

    def peek(self):
        return self.items[0] if not self.is_empty() else None
```

