CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) error tab aata hai jab aapki web application ek domain se doosre domain pe request bhejti hai, aur server ne is request ko allow nahi kiya. Ye security feature hai jo browsers ko different origins se requests ko restrict karta hai. 

