Caching ek technique hai jisme hum frequently accessed data ko temporary storage mein rakhte hain taake jab bhi us data ki zaroorat ho to usay jaldi se access kiya ja sake. Ye performance ko bohat behtar banata hai kyunki data ko baar baar source se nahi lana parta. Misal ke taur pe, agar aapki website pe ek image hai jo aksar dikhayi jati hai, to agar aap us image ko cache kar lein, to wo pehli dafa load hone ke baad har dafa local cache se load hogi. Isse loading time bohat kam ho jata hai. 

Example: 

```javascript
// JavaScript mein caching ka example
const cache = {};

function fetchData(url) {
    if (cache[url]) {
        return Promise.resolve(cache[url]); // agar data cache mein hai to seedha return karein
    }
    return fetch(url).then(response => response.json()).then(data => {
        cache[url] = data; // naye data ko cache mein daal den
        return data;
    });
}
```

