Recursion ek aisi technique hai jismein ek function apne aap ko call karta hai. Ye tab kaam karti hai jab aap kisi maslay ko chote hisson mein todna chahte hain. Har call ke sath, aapko base case specify karna chahiye jahan aap recursion ko rok dena chahte hain. Misal ke taur par, factorial function ko samajhte hain: 

