Database normalization ek process hai jo data ko is tarah se organize karta hai ke redundancy kam ho sake aur data integrity barqarar rahe. Ismein kuch rules follow kiye jaate hain jise hum 'normal forms' kehte hain. Pehli normal form (1NF) kehti hai ke har column mein sirf atomic values honi chahiye. Dusri normal form (2NF) ka matlab hai ke har non-key attribute ko primary key se fully depend hona chahiye. Yahan ek example hai:

```sql
