Recursion ek programming technique hai jisme ek function apne aap ko call karta hai. Ye kaam is tarah se karta hai ke ek base case hota hai jahan function call khatam hota hai, aur recursive case jahan function khud ko call karta hai. 

Example: Factorial function jo recursion ka use karta hai: 
``` 
function factorial(n) {
    if (n === 0) {
        return 1; // Base case
    } else {
        return n * factorial(n - 1); // Recursive case
    }
}
console.log(factorial(5)); // Output: 120
``` 
