Caching aik technique hai jisse hum data ko temporarily store karte hain taake future requests par us data ko jaldi se access kiya ja sake. Yeh performance ko improve karta hai aur server par load ko kam karta hai. Jab bhi koi user kisi resource ko pehli dafa access karta hai, toh wo resource cache mein store ho jata hai. Jab wo user dobara us resource ko request karega, toh yeh cache se directly load hota hai, jo ke time aur resources dono bachata hai. 

Example: Agar aap ek web application bana rahe hain jo data ko database se fetch karta hai, toh aap caching use kar sakte hain. 

```python
# Example of caching in Python using a simple dictionary
cache = {}

def fetch_data_from_db(query):
    if query in cache:
        return cache[query]  # Return cached data
    else:
        data = database.fetch(query)  # Fetch from DB
        cache[query] = data  # Store in cache
        return data
```

