DRY ka matlab hai 'Don't Repeat Yourself'. Ye principle encourage karta hai ke agar kisi code ka part bar-bar use hota hai, to usay ek jagah par likha jaye. Is se code clean aur maintainable rehta hai. Ek example dekho:

