Python decorators functions ya methods ko wrap karne ka tariqa hain, jisse unki functionality ko modify kiya ja sakta hai. Ye ek higher-order function hain jo ek function ko input lete hain aur naya function return karte hain. Iska istemal logging, access control, ya code reuse ke liye hota hai.

