2. **Data Transfer**: HTTP mein data sirf request-responses ke through transfer hota hai, jabke WebSocket mein aap server aur client ke beech bina kisi additional request ke data bhej sakte hain.

3. **Use Cases**: HTTP ka istemal simple requests ke liye hota hai, jaise webpages load karna, lekin WebSocket ka istemal real-time applications, jaise chat applications ya live notifications ke liye hota hai.

