Binary search algorithm sorted array mein istemal hota hai aur ye search karne ka kaam bahut tezi se karta hai. Iska tareeqa ye hai ke ye mid element ko check karta hai aur dekhte hai ke woh element search kiye gaye value se chota hai ya bada. Agar mid element match hota hai to search complete ho jati hai. Agar nahi, to half portion ko search karte hain. Yahan ek simple example hai:

```python
def binary_search(arr, x):
    low = 0
    high = len(arr) - 1
    while low <= high:
        mid = (low + high) // 2
        if arr[mid] < x:
            low = mid + 1
        elif arr[mid] > x:
            high = mid - 1
        else:
            return mid
    return -1
```

Is function mein, agar element nahi milta to -1 return hota hai. Ye algorithm O(log n) time complexity ke saath kaam karta hai, jo ke isse bahut efficient banata hai.

