JavaScript mein variables declare karne ke liye hum let, const aur var ka istemal karte hain.

1. **var**: Ye purana tareeqa hai variables declare karne ka. Ye function scope hota hai, matlab agar aap ise function ke andar declare karte hain to ye sirf us function ke andar hi accessible hoga. Example:
