Unit testing ek aisi practice hai jisme aap apne code ke chote chote hisson (units) ko alag se test karte hain. Iska maqsad yeh hai ke aap jaan saken ke har unit sahi tarah se kaam kar raha hai ya nahi. Yeh zaroori hai kyunki yeh aapko bugs ko shuru mein hi pakarne mein madad karta hai, jisse software ki quality behtar hoti hai. 

Example: Agar aapko ek function likhna hai jo do numbers ko add kare, toh aap uska unit test kuch is tarah kar sakte hain:

