HTTP methods web development mein kaafi important hain. Inka istemal data ko server se ya server par bhejne ke liye hota hai. 

1. **GET**: Yeh method server se data retrieve karne ke liye hota hai. Iska istemal sirf data dekhne ke liye kiya jata hai. 
   - Example: 
   ```
   fetch('https://api.example.com/data')
