Python decorators aik special function hain jo kisi dusre function ko modify karte hain. Ye aapko function ki functionality ko extend karne ki permission dete hain bina us function ko modify kiye. Yeh ek syntax sugar hai jo aapko readable aur clean code likhne mein madad karti hai. Iska istemal karne ka tareeqa ye hai:

```python
def my_decorator(func):
