Stack ek linear data structure hai jo Last In First Out (LIFO) ka principle follow karta hai. Iska matlab ye hai ke jo item last mein add hota hai, wo pehle remove hota hai. Stack mein do main operations hote hain: `push` (item add karna) aur `pop` (item remove karna). Yahan ek example hai: 

```python
class Stack:
    def __init__(self):
        self.items = []

    def push(self, item):
        self.items.append(item)

    def pop(self):
        return self.items.pop() if not self.is_empty() else None

    def is_empty(self):
        return len(self.items) == 0

my_stack = Stack()
my_stack.push(10)
my_stack.push(20)
print(my_stack.pop())  # Output: 20
```

