Caching ek technique hai jisme hum frequently accessed data ko temporarily store karte hain taake jab bhi wo data zaroorat ho, to use jaldi se access kiya ja sake. Ye performance ko behter banata hai kyunke data ko baar baar database ya dusri sources se nahi lena padta. Misal ke taur par, agar aap ek web application bana rahe hain, to aap user ke profile data ko cache kar sakte hain. Is se load time kam hota hai. 

