Python generators aise functions hain jo ek waqt par ek value return karte hain aur jab next value ki zarurat hoti hai toh wapas aate hain. Yield keyword ke zariye aap generator bana sakte hain. Yeh memory efficient hain kyunki yeh saari values ek saath memory mein nahi rakhte, balki on-the-fly generate karte hain. 

Example: 
Agar aapko ek generator function banana hai jo 0 se le kar n tak numbers return kare, toh aap aise kar sakte hain:

```python
def my_generator(n):
    for i in range(n):
        yield i

for value in my_generator(5):
    print(value)  # Output: 0, 1, 2, 3, 4
```
